[32m+[m[32m## Privacy[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mPDF Unlocker does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal data.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mAll PDF processing is performed locally on your device. No files are uploaded to any server, and no account or internet connection is required to use the app.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mPDF Unlocker works entirely on your device.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m* No data is uploaded.[m
[32m+[m[32m* No cloud processing.[m
[32m+[m[32m* No analytics.[m
[32m+[m[32m* No tracking.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Assets & Attribution[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe application icon was created with the assistance of AI image generation tools and may contain similarities to other generated artwork. It is used in good faith for this open-source project.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIf you believe any asset used in this project infringes upon your rights, please open an issue on GitHub or contact the maintainer, and the matter will be reviewed promptly.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Download[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mDownload the latest APK from the GitHub Releases page.[m
[32m+[m
 ## Project[m
 [m
 GitHub: https://github.com/OpenAppex/pdfunlocker[m
