[36m@@ -0,0 +1,12 @@[m
[32m+[m[32mPDF Unlocker is a free and open-source Android application that removes password protection from PDF files you are authorized to access.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mFeatures:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m• Unlock password-protected PDFs[m
[32m+[m[32m• Offline processing[m
[32m+[m[32m• No account required[m
[32m+[m[32m• Privacy friendly[m
[32m+[m[32m• Open source[m
[32m+[m[32m• Material Design interface[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mAll PDF processing happens locally on your device. No files are uploaded to any server.[m
